Articles.Content:
GSF-2 is a two seat spaceplane able to get to orbit and then to the moon or minmus orbits without refueling. Has docking ports both top and bottom so you can attach addition fuel engines or even little landers to.

Below are some pics, and youtube link to show you how to get it into orbit.

http://youtu.be/R37_FoXXCck

Download craft file here: https://mega.co.nz/#!GIVyCR7Z!HoeTUkPuGDigbEGYf08ZRABB45RkF4Tv5rsp7mUe9yw

or Here: https://docs.google.com/file/d/0BxW31U5ogVX-djVySzNmcHVSdk0/edit?usp=sharing

Action Keys:

1 = Inside Turbofans

2 = Outside Turbofans

3 = LV-N engine

4 = 48-7S Engine

5 = Intake Group 1

6 = Intake Group 2

7 = Intake Group 3

8 = Intake Group 4
